OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,FA group of primary school students in
OL,7,FKent have been named Britain's
OL,8,Ffunniest class by the Beano comic book.
OL,10,FYear 6 students from Joy Lane Primary
OL,11,FSchool, in Whitstable, were praised by
OL,12,Fjudges for their 'genuinely hilarious'
OL,13,Fjoke.
OL,15,FThe competition saw hundreds of
OL,16,Fclasses send in lines they'd written
OL,17,Ffor judging by an expert panel of
OL,18,FBeano writers and the public.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
