PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781097082
OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,F"The winning joke was inventive and
OL,7,Fgenuinely hilarious. Clearly, the
OL,8,Ffuture of comedy is in safe hands with
OL,9,FBoyce class," said Mike Stirling,
OL,10,FDirector of Mischief at Beano.
OL,12,FHe added: "All of Beano's best bits
OL,13,Fcome directly from kids, championing
OL,14,Fchildhood in all its playful
OL,15,Fbrilliance and making reading the most
OL,16,Fmischievous thing that they can do!
OL,18,F"This competition is just one of the
OL,19,Fways Beano brings extra fun to summer
OL,20,Fwhile showcasing the next wave of
OL,21,Fcheeky comedy talent."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
