CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781097082
OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,FFor their winning gag, Boyce Class
OL,7,Fstudents and their teacher, Ms Crowe,
OL,8,Fwill feature in the Beano comic by the
OL,9,Fartist Nigel Parkinson.
OL,11,FThe competition, now in its eighth
OL,12,Fyear, is run to bring a sense of fun
OL,13,Fand irreverence to the classroom and
OL,14,Fhelp boost children's confidence at
OL,15,Fthe same time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
