PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1781097082
OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,F"I'm a big advocate for education,
OL,7,Fincluding plenty of enjoyment, and not
OL,8,Fmany people get the chance to share a
OL,9,Flaugh not just with their classmates,
OL,10,Fbut with people from all around the
OL,11,Fnation!," said Ms Crowe.
OL,13,FShe added: "Britain's Funniest Class
OL,14,Fis such a great competition for
OL,15,Fencouraging humour, inspiring
OL,16,Fcreativity, and helping children grow
OL,17,Fin confidence."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
