OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,FThis year, the competition has also
OL,7,Fjoined forced with Place2Be, a
OL,8,Fchildren's mental health charity, to
OL,9,Fcreate a lesson for teachers focused
OL,10,Fon fun, belonging, and coming together
OL,11,Fthrough laughter.
OL,13,F"Laughter can play an important role
OL,14,Fin supporting children's wellbeing,
OL,15,Fhelping to ease stress and boost
OL,16,Fconfidence," said Dr Rebecca
OL,17,FKirkbride, Place2Be's Clinical
OL,18,FDirector.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
