OL,3,CPrimary students crowned Britain's
OL,4,Cfunniest class by Beano
OL,6,F"Sharing jokes gives young people a
OL,7,Fsimple way to connect, creating
OL,8,Fenvironments where everyone feels
OL,9,Fincluded and valued," she added.
OL,11,F"It helps friendships grow, encourages
OL,12,Fa sense of belonging, and makes it
OL,13,Feasier for children to navigate
OL,14,Feveryday challenges."
